WHEN THE NEXT STEP IN YOUR CAREER LEADS YOU TO THINK OF BUSINESS OWNERSHIP...
Consider Regis Corporation, the global leader in hair services and products. We franchise hair salons and hair care brands in an industry with the distinction of providing consumer services fundamental in any community and any economic climate.Leverage the knowledge we’ve gained with over 90+ years in the salon business. Regis Corporation currently operates over 9,000 hair salons and related haircare businesses.We invite you to learn as much as you can about our franchise opportunities, and feel free to contact us if you want to discuss any aspects of Regis.











         
 
